; Coverage for amount.cc lines 204, 209, 211, 220:
; Very large amounts exercise the thousands separator loop multiple times,
; ensuring the comma separator (line 220) and decimal point (line 204)
; are both covered. Multiple digit groups force multiple separator insertions.

commodity $
    format $1,000.00

2024/01/01 Huge Purchase
    Expenses:Capital   $1,234,567.89
    Assets:Bank

test bal Expenses
       $1,234,567.89  Expenses:Capital
end test
